Coal India Issues 10-Year Overseas Tender, India Coal Watch Says

-- B y   D i n a k a r   S e t h u r a m a n
-- 
2011-05-13T07:25:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/coal-india-issues-10-year-overseas-tender-india-coal-watch-says.html
Coal India Ltd. (COAL)  issued a tender last
week to purchase coal from overseas for 10 years, India Coal
Market Watch said, citing the company’s Chairman N.C. Jha.  Deliveries are to start in six months to a year, the
industry newsletter said. Potential suppliers have three weeks
to submit their offers, according to India Coal Market Watch.
Volumes aren’t final yet, it said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Dinakar Sethuraman in Singapore at 
